        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-7">
            <p class="welcome-text">Welcome</p>
            <p class="sub-text">Thank you for your
                interest in our beta program.</p>
            <p class="paragraph-text">BUZ is the premiere mobile and web app that makes it simple to book your next
                barber appointment. Our goal
                is to streamline the barbershop experience and drive traffic to local barbers in the most efficient way
                possible. </p>
        </div>
